---
const cards = [
  {
    title: "We Know the USA Market",
    desc: "Finkeepers bring in the deep knowledge of the USA markets - their tax laws and regulations, and compliance and shifts. Hence, having a temporary CFO for your firm from Finkeepers will be a helpful hand and will easily ease into the routine of the firm. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Curated Strategies",
    desc: "Leveraging the expertise, the temporary CFO services of Finkeepers will be curated according to the needs of the firm, rather than applying generic and basic strategies. We understand that when it comes to making financial decisions, one size fits all is never an option.",
  },
  {
    title: "Actionable Solutions",
    desc: "The solutions provided by Finkeepers will not be fictional. Those will all be in regulation with market shifts, suggested after doing competitor analysis, and will deliver results instead of incurring losses, which small businesses cannot afford. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Support During Crisis",
    desc: "We do not abandon our own during times of need. Finkeepers will support small businesses of the USA during the time of crisis and help resurface them and make correct financial decisions. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Proven Track Record",
    desc: "Finkeepers have been helping small businesses in the USA survive the market and make profits with the help of temporary CFO services. WE streamline finances and establish systems that run long after the subscription period is over.",
  },
  
];
---

<div
  class="main-container w-full pt-[80px] pr-[20px] pb-[80px] pl-[20px] lg:pr-[120px] lg:pl-[120px] flex flex-col gap-[32px] justify-center items-center bg-[#106253] relative mx-auto"
>
  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex justify-center items-center">
    <span
      class="font-['Inter'] text-[24px] sm:text-[28px] md:text-[32px] lg:text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.2] text-white"
    >
     Why Choose Finkeepers as your Temporary CFOs?

    </span>
  </div>
 <div>
  <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#ffffff] max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        Finkeepers, being the team of bookkeeping experts in the USA, will help you take all the
financial load off of you, which will allow you to focus on things of dire importance and urgency.
      </p>
  </div>
  <!-- Cards Container -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex flex-col gap-[25px]">
    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]">
      {
        cards.slice(0, 3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#106253] rounded-[16px] border border-white shadow-[0_1px_11.1px_0_rgba(237,124,0,0.16)] p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
            <div class="flex w-[50px] h-[50px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-semibold text-[24px] leading-[28px]">
                {index + 1}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px]">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white font-medium text-[16px] leading-[22px]">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]">
      {
        cards.slice(3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#106253] rounded-[16px] border border-white shadow-[0_1px_11.1px_0_rgba(237,124,0,0.16)] p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
            <div class="flex w-[50px] h-[50px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-semibold text-[24px] leading-[28px]">
                {index + 4}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px]">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white font-medium text-[16px] leading-[22px]">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
